name: Rose Finance
additional_notices: No active trades are found for this coin. Please submit a ticket at %{link} if you think this is an error.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Rose Finance is a fork of tomb finance on arbitrum.

What makes your project unique?
Rather than focusing on pegg strategy, Rose Finance offer a Debase model.

History of your project.
With most of our team members having been part of the crypto space since 2018, we have a strong belief in the potential of DeFi in this space.
As a team, we recognized the need and potential to launch a unique Tomb fork on Arbitrum, unlike anything seen before in the industry.

What’s next for your project?
Launching on Mainnet on March 20th 

What can your token be used for?
It's a Dao token with debase functionality.
